<p>4H昨日技术性调整到位后空头延续，目前短期均线发散向下，MACD零轴下方死叉运行，短线技术性调整后有望维持震荡下行。</p>
<p><img class="img-responsive alignnone size-full wp-image-67555" src="https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪22.png" alt="" width="1846" height="661" srcset="https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪22.png 1846w, https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪22-300x107.png 300w, https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪22-768x275.png 768w, https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪22-1024x367.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1846px) 100vw, 1846px" /></p>
<p>1H昨日下破1.2310一线偏空，今日上方关注1.2320-30一线阻力，保持在此下方有望继续测试前支撑。</p>
<p>从上行方向看，上方阻力1.2330，1.2380,1.2430，从下行方向看，下方支撑1.2260,1.2210,1.2160.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>现货金：</p>
