<p><img class="img-responsive alignnone size-full wp-image-67548" src="https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪2-1.png" alt="" width="1846" height="661" srcset="https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪2-1.png 1846w, https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪2-1-300x107.png 300w, https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪2-1-768x275.png 768w, https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/栾雪2-1-1024x367.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1846px) 100vw, 1846px" /></p>
